member.summary:
Update specific table in the data set. all fields must be wrriten in the sql statment for insert and update. the order of the wrriten fields is according to order they were selected by the select statment. i.e ,select * : the order is according to the fields order in the table.
Notes: 1. You must not use NOW() in the queries, you should set the DateTime fields directly in the data table. If you use NOW() concurreny exception is thrown. 2. an integer field in the db is refered to int16. if you pass as a parameter integer(the default is int32) you will get overflow error.
